<H3> <TI>   `Document of Pledge and Accord' Signed in Aden </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN1801163694 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1500 GMT 18 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1801163694 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In an atmosphere of happiness and optimism, the 
document of pledge and accord to build the new Yemeni state was 
initialed this morning. The signing took place during the final 
session of the Political Forces Dialogue Committee held in Aden, 
the economic and trade capital, this morning. 
  Prime Minister Haydar Abu-Bakr al-'Attas opened the session 
with a speech in which he noted that, with God's help and thanks 
