<F P=102>  JN1901145594 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1215 GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1901145594 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At 1145 today, President Hafiz al-Asad received 
Lebanese President Ilyas al-Hirawi, Chamber of Deputies Speaker 
Nabih Birri, Prime Minister Rafiq al-Hariri, Foreign Minister 
Faris Buwayz, and Chief Lebanese Negotiator Suhayl Shammas. 
  Vice President 'Abd-al-Halim Khaddam, Foreign Minister Faruq 
al-Shar', and Nasir Qaddur, the minister of state for foreign 
affairs, also attended the meeting. 

</TEXT>

