<H3> <TI>   Amal-Israel Clashes Occur in Southern Areas </TI></H3>
<H4>   Amal Attacks Israeli, Militia Posts </H4>
<F P=102> NC1501093894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 15 Jan 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1501093894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Amal Movement has announced that on the 
anniversary of the martyrdom of one of its members, Abu-Jamal, 
one of its groups attacked an Israeli occupation forces' 
position on Hula hill at 0630 today, using automatic weapons and 
rockets. Subsequently, the enemy forces shelled Shaqra and 
Bra'shit, using 120-mm artillery. 
  The Amal Movement also announced that one of its groups last 
night attacked an agent militia position on al-Shumariyah hill, 
using automatic weapons and rockets. The resistance fighters 
hit an observation tower and destroyed the position's 
fortifications. 

</TEXT>

