<H3> <TI>   House Arrest Measures Lifted; Detainees Released </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1901165794 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1600 
GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1901165794 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] [Announcer] I have just heard that the Ministry of 
Interior and Local Communities has announced the immediate 
lifting of the measures concerning house arrest at the national 
level, and the release of people detained at the two security 
centers in Oued Namous and in Amguel. 
  The decision comes within the framework of the openness 
[infiraj] measures to facilitate the success of the national 
dialogue, the Ministry of Interior and Local Communities' 
statement said. 

</TEXT>

