<H3> <TI>   Officials React to Document of Pledge, Accord </TI></H3>
<H4>   Salih, al-Bid Approve Document </H4>
<F P=102> JN1901203394 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
2000 GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1901203394 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, 
chairman of the Presidential Council, and 'Ali Salim al-Bid, 
vice chairman of the Presidential Council, have blessed and 
approved the Document of Pledge and Accord. They gave the 
committee full authority to set a date and venue for the final 
endorsement of the document. This took place when the brother 
chairman and vice chairman received the committee. 
  This was stated by brother Ahmad Salim 'Afif, the rapporteur 
of the committee entrusted by the Political Forces Dialogue 
Committee to follow up the implementation of the seventh 
paragraph of the Document of Pledge and Accord. 
  Brother Ahmad Jabir 'Afif added that the committee will hold 
its next meeting tomorrow morning to draft a program. Then it 
will show it to the brother chairman and vice chairman. 

</TEXT>

