Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat returned to 
Tunisia last night after a brief visit to Egypt. During his 
visit he met President Husni Mubarak and the U.S. commerce 
secretary to discuss the outcome of the Palestinian-Israeli 
talks on arrangements for self-rule and the U.S. contribution 
