head of the Palestinian team negotiating with Israel, said that 
'Arafat will most probably return to Cairo on Sunday [23 
January] after meeting Israeli Foreign Affairs Minister Shim'on 
Peres tomorrow. Both men will be in Oslo to attend the funeral 
of the Norwegian foreign affairs minister. 

