<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' this morning 
received a mixed Democratic and Republican Congressional team 
led by Mr. Tom Lantos. Dr. Majdi al-Jazzar, chief of the U.S. 
Desk, and the U.S. charges d'affaires in Damascus were present 
