<F P=100> Egypt </F>
<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Arrives in Cairo To Discuss Peace Process </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2001074394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0727 GMT 20 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2001074394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 20 Jan (MENA)--Palestinian president Yasir 
'Arafat arrived in Cairo this morning on a visit to Egypt. 
During his visit, he will meet President Husni Mubarak to 
discuss the latest developments in the peace process and the 
Palestinian-Israeli negotiations. 'Arafat's visit comes within 
the framework of efforts to overcome the obstacles impeding the 
implementation of the Palestinian-Israeli Declaration of 
Principles and the Gaza-Jericho Agreement. 

</TEXT>

