<H3> <TI>   Rally for Culture, Democracy To Boycott </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2301204294 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 23 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2301204294 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] We heard a short while ago that the leadership of 
the Rally for Culture and Democracy [RCD] announced that the 
party will not take part in the national conference [scheduled 
to take place on 25 January]. 
  However, the RCD has pointed out that the reason behind this 
decision was that the adopted platform on the transitional 
period to be discussed by the national conference contains a 
retraction from the one proposed by the Higher State Council. 

</TEXT>

