<F P=100> ARAB AFRICA </F>
<F P=101> Algeria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Nahnah Wants FIS in Islamic Republican Rally </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2001202194 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 20 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2001202194 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] After the call of Algerian scholars and 
preachers for a meeting this Thursday for a conference entitled 
Reconciliation is Good, a large crowd complied with the call and 
came to Harcha Hall in Algiers. In this meeting, the Islamic 
Republican Rally [Tajammu' Islami Jumhuri] was set up. [passage 
omitted]. 
  [Begin Cheikh Mahfouz Nahnah, chairman of the Islamic 
Society 
Movement -- HAMAS -- recording] It is the Islamic Republican 
Rally and its acronym is TAJ [crown]. We want to have under 
this TAJ scholars, preachers, the FIS [Islamic Salvation Front], 
regardless of whether it was dissolved or not, the al-Nahdah, 
the Umma [Party], and all the patriotic people who have 
integrity and all the men of Algeria who want to form a bulwark 
against the factors of fragmentation. [end recording] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
