<F P=100> Libya </F>
<H3> <TI>   General People's Congress Continues Work </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2401102794 Tripoli JANA in English 0805 GMT 24 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2401102794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Surt, Ay Annar [January] 24, JAMAHIRYA NEWS 
AGENCY--The general meeting of the people's congresses, the 
people's committees, unions, syndicates and professional 
associations - the General People's Congress - last night 
resumed its proceedings in the city of Surt to formulate the 
decisions of the basic people's congresses of their 2nd session 
for 1403 A.P.D. 
  The five committees, set up by the congress, including the 
committees of laws, the committee of follow up and reports, the 
committee of public affairs the committee of foreign policy and 
the committee of budget and trilateral programme resumed the 
sorting out of the decisions of the basic people's congresses 
putting them under the appropriate items and reading out and 
debating the remarks coming from the basic people's congresses 
for approval in their final form. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

